  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: Let It Be, Leave It Alone
---
Cloud Chief said, "The Heavenly Master has favored me with this Virtue,
instructed me in this Silence. All my life I have been looking for it,
and now at last I have it!" He bowed his head twice, stood up, took his
leave, and went away.
